  "detailed_description": "<h1>Check out</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ADD TO WISHLIST</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/232a5d5216c0a8833f151c04ac2d9e4c.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/232a5d5216c0a8833f151c04ac2d9e4c.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/232a5d5216c0a8833f151c04ac2d9e4c.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Story</u>: Andrei moved to Moscow for work and rented an apartment in a panel house, which suited his budget. Soon, living in the apartment, he began to notice strange things happening every night. Somebody knocks on the door or it just opens by itself, then in the middle of the night strange sounds and voices wake me up. During the day everything seemed to go back to normal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The landlady forgot to warn that Andrei would have neighbors cohabiting with him in the same apartment. She warned him only after moving in, leaving a note saying that he should behave quietly and not make noise, and not to go where he shouldn't.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the center of the story - the apartment, where the main action of the game takes place. Here Andrew meets strange neighbors who lived in the apartment before him. Waking up in the middle of the night, Andrei observes the neighbors, exploring the locked rooms and studying the notes they left behind. Just like that, he finds himself stuck in this apartment, which used to seem like cheap housing in an old Soviet building.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/e6801a28cd52fba2494e58b2f5277b13.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/e6801a28cd52fba2494e58b2f5277b13.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/e6801a28cd52fba2494e58b2f5277b13.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Game Features</u>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A typical plot in the current worldly realities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A game in the genre of “walking simulator”.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The passage of no more than an hour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Uncover the frightening secrets of mysterious neighbors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Meet the consequences of the revealed secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Soviet apartment atmosphere in our time.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Story</u>: Andrei moved to Moscow for work and rented an apartment in a panel house, which suited his budget. Soon, living in the apartment, he began to notice strange things happening every night. Somebody knocks on the door or it just opens by itself, then in the middle of the night strange sounds and voices wake me up. During the day everything seemed to go back to normal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/69e5845a0a83368df5d4936af3f46bca.mp4?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The landlady forgot to warn that Andrei would have neighbors cohabiting with him in the same apartment. She warned him only after moving in, leaving a note saying that he should behave quietly and not make noise, and not to go where he shouldn't.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.poster.avif?t=1743531077\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.webm?t=1743531077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265370/extras/dd0ad0e72a508d10f81a5513b0aa632d.mp4?t=174353107